          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Her upbringing had given her an independence of mind that made her more like a girl of today than one of her own time - which was why she had walked out, and why she was not daunted by the prospect of being alone.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
